{"tid":1105651,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"國情了解 國慶幾號 國歌點唱都唔識 好打極有限","createTime":"2019-04-14T05:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T18:21:32.000Z","uid":208927,"like":87,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f412b818d3fa6b1857f347caef91687d138e82","tid":1105651,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:19:16.000Z","msg":"就黎國慶喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日就同大家介紹一下國慶同國歌<br />\n了解一下國情<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國慶：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實大英帝國冇一個正式嘅國慶日<br />\n差不多嘅日子就係女王生日（ Queen&rsquo;s Official Birthday)<br />\n但呢一個並非事頭婆真實生日日期<br />\n（其實事頭婆下個星期日4月21號93歲大壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n而係一個日子俾國民同殖民地慶祝皇室嘅日子<br />\n由18世紀開始有 Queen&rsquo;s/ King&rsquo;s official Birthday<br />\n而近年就設係六月嘅第二個星期六<br />\n今年就係6月8日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cchxtI14eJ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcchxtI14eJ4&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8sLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=3860d369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cchxtI14eJ4</a><br />\n女皇90大壽慶祝片段<br />\n<br />\n噤點解講就黎國慶呢？<br />\n大英帝國冇正式國慶姐<br />\n但英格蘭/蘇格蘭/威爾斯同北愛爾蘭有自己國慶日<br />\n係按國家嘅主保聖人嘅節日而定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7Zo7JK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7Zo7JK.png&h=e3ff271e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而英格蘭嘅主保Saint George節日就係4月23日<br />\n（有關Saint George嘅故事可以遲啲開post)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJ0vNMx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJ0vNMx.png&h=5fdfccf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英格蘭國旗又被稱為Saint George&rsquo;s Cross<br />\n獅心王帶領十字軍東征就係效法St George嘅勇氣<br />\n<del>打9啲蛔光復耶路撒冷</del><br />\n之後St George就取代左聖愛得華做英格蘭主保<br />\n<br />\n順便講下Scotland/ Wales/ Northern Ireland嘅國慶日<br />\nSCOTLAND 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁳󠁣󠁴󠁿: 11月30 St Andres&rsquo;s Day<br />\nWALES🏴󠁧󠁢󠁷󠁬󠁳󠁿 : 3月1 St David&rsquo;s Day<br />\nNORTHERN IRELAND: 3月17 St Patrick&rsquo;s Day<br />\n( 與美國St Patrick&rsquo;s day相同，美國白人多來自愛爾蘭）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國歌：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n天佑女王（設英文歌詞）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/haI8HMjlE9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhaI8HMjlE9s&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8sLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=3d97ddf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/haI8HMjlE9s</a><br />\n（小弟之前edit的，有時間可以edit其他歌 ie I vow for thee my country/ Jerusalem，鍾意可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n中文歌詞：<br />\n<br />\n（等一段）              <br />\n上帝保佑女皇，      <br />\n祝她萬壽無疆，          <br />\n天佑女王！            <br />\n常勝利，沐榮光；      <br />\n孚民望，心歡暢；     <br />\n治國家，王運長；     <br />\n天佑女王！<br />\n<br />\n（第二段）<br />\n揚神威，張天網，<br />\n保王室，殲敵方，<br />\n一鼓滌蕩。<br />\n破陰謀，滅奸党，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（有語境）</span><br />\n把亂盟一掃光；<br />\n讓我們齊仰望，<br />\n天佑女王！<br />\n<br />\n（第三段）<br />\n願上帝恩澤長，<br />\n選精品，傾寶囊，<br />\n萬歲女王！<br />\n願她捍衛國法，<br />\n使民心齊歸向，<br />\n一致衷心歌唱，<br />\n天佑女王！<br />\n<br />\n(歌詞摘至維基百科）<br />\n<br />\n（ btw search過有人清唱中文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過唔建議聽）<br />\n<br />\n國歌係從1745年起沿用<br />\n會因君主性別而命為<br />\nGod save the King/ Queen<br />\n當然歌詞都會轉She-&gt; He/ Her-&gt; His<br />\n完整國歌有4段<br />\n不過第4段極少使用<br />\n儀式上大部分時候其實都係唱第一段<br />\n大活動指到要唱國歌就會唱晒3段<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以更了解國情<br />\n俾人問唔會囗啞啞<br />\n有興趣遲啲可以講下其他Topic<br />\n1. Church of England （ Henry VIII )<br />\n2. The troubles（愛爾蘭脫英/IRA）<br />\n3. St George 的故事<br />\n4. 愛國歌曲 I vow for thee my country<br />\n5. 愛國歌曲 Jerusalem<br />\n6. 愛國歌曲 Land of hope and glory"},{"pid":"78aa0687ceccb84990b0213986f2c5084e2189ae","tid":1105651,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"ff6ffe35df1b04b1a69da50f8c0d9162eb0e5da4","tid":1105651,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:33:38.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"84262d4fc639210c1bf0642b0c722ab494b9620d","tid":1105651,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"d3c412bf5aac75220fc3d2b4dc6640468e572efc","tid":1105651,"uid":189453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:46:33.000Z","msg":"問下女王可唔可以比英國籍我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b593fc222aa6f95d5f91c370f4973e0b94e54a","tid":1105651,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:53:35.000Z","msg":"好文要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8e824dccb877528605ceb7feda5aab9a33f26b","tid":1105651,"uid":208927,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d3c412bf5aac75220fc3d2b4dc6640468e572efc","tid":1105651,"uid":189453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:46:33.000Z","msg":"問下女王可唔可以比英國籍我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"攞個BNO去當幾年兵囉<br />\n英國當兵其實好多野玩<br />\n生活包健康<br />\n有得食有得住<br />\n有時又可以出trip去滑雪/浮潛<br />\n退休又有長糧<br />\n比起9成國家當兵好<br />\n死人其實好少<br />\n都係病同少部分自殺（army多）<br />\nBC可以從以下途徑：<br />\n一係你父母之前讀好書<br />\n一係你去當兵<br />\n一係喺個到有專業工作留幾年<br />\n一係投資移民<br />\n一係溝鬼妹"},{"pid":"be71a51d61008533f68831eefa706ed4d86fbca2","tid":1105651,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50b593fc222aa6f95d5f91c370f4973e0b94e54a","tid":1105651,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:53:35.000Z","msg":"好文要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝"},{"pid":"4b7a2a20c31ade063d